What that?

256
00:14:33,083 --> 00:14:34,166
Come on up.

257
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:35,333
We're trying!

258
00:14:35,416 --> 00:14:37,875
Hey, watch where
you're stepping.

259
00:14:37,958 --> 00:14:38,666
Quiet, everyone!

260
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:39,500
Yes?

261
00:14:39,583 --> 00:14:42,250
Let's do a show!

262
00:14:42,333 --> 00:14:43,958
Hi, guys!

263
00:14:44,041 --> 00:14:47,291
So it's all ours. The day after
tomorrow we'll be performing

264
00:14:47,375 --> 00:14:49,500
on the Marine Park's stage.

265
00:14:49,583 --> 00:14:52,208
As you can tell, we don't
have a lot of time to prepare.

266
00:14:52,291 --> 00:14:54,083
So, if any of you
have any suggestions

